      "content": "While some wellness groups advocate for loading protocols, your personal health profile matters, and risks vary between individuals even if you are generally healthy. Safe supplementation depends on factors like your baseline levels and potential sensitivities, which only a medical professional can assess with testing. For the most personalized and safest approach, consulting a doctor is the best way to tailor a \"quick boost\" regimen to your specific needs.",
      "source": "target",
