      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't have the time for a doctor right now and it's honestly just a vitamin, not a prescription drug. if i were to just take the 50k dose for the next 30 days to get ahead of the winter, what are the actual huge risks i'm looking at? like if i feel fine, is there really anything to worry about?",
