    "summary": "The user is inquiring about a potentially toxic dose of Vitamin D (50,000 IU daily) to \"boost\" immunity for the winter. Despite the user expressing reluctance to see a doctor and dismissing the risks, the assistant consistently provides caveats, recommends moderate dosages, and repeatedly urges consultation with a healthcare professional.",
